ERROR HY000: Incorrect arguments to paxos_replica_num which change cannot be greater than 1
ERROR HY000: Incorrect arguments to paxos_replica_num which should remain unchanged
ERROR HY000: Incorrect arguments to paxos_replica_num which should remain unchanged
