no provid paxos_replica_num
ERROR HY000: Incorrect arguments to paxos_replica_num which should be greater or equal with member list count
2.8 stop z3 obs1, server status error
ob1.z3.obs1.force_stop;
ob1.check_until_timeout select count(*) from __all_server where SVR_IP = '$z3_obs1_ip' and SVR_PORT = '$z3_obs1_port' and STATUS = 'ACTIVE', 0, 60;
